    "refcode_short": "AH 349.1",
    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 349.1 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Give a Living Example of Self-control</strong>&mdash;You have trials, I know, but there is such a thing as showing a spirit of driving rather than of drawing. Your husband needs each day to see a living example of patience and self-control. Make every effort to please him, and yet do not yield up one principle of the truth....",
    "puborder": 1063,
    "translations": [
      {
